@startuml
title UC09 - View Statistics Leaderboard Sequence
actor Visitor
participant "Web UI" as UI
participant "Statistics API" as API
participant "Statistics Service" as Svc
database "DB" as DB
Visitor -> UI : Open statistics/leaderboard
UI -> API : GET /statistics or /leaderboard
API -> Svc : getAggregates(scope)
Svc -> DB : query Statistic, Prediction, User points
DB --> Svc : aggregate data
Svc --> API : statistic DTOs
API --> UI : 200 OK
UI --> Visitor : Display results
@enduml
